{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solveTrivialConjuncts\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">solveTrivialConjuncts</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Solves conjunctions whose leaves are `True` or `e₁ = e₂`, and returns a residual goal containing\nexactly the conjuncts that could not be solved.\nThis procedure may assign metavariables in `e₁`/`e₂`, for example for `e = ?m` it will assign\n`?m := e`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solveTrivialConjuncts","kind":"opaque","line":148,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solveTrivialConjuncts","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L148-L188"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introsExcessArgs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">introsExcessArgs</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Introduce the excess state arguments of an entailment goal `pre ⊑ rhs` whose lattice type is a\nfunction type `σ₁ → … → σₙ → α`: repeatedly apply `stateArgIntro` (a backward rule for\n`Lean.Order.le_of_forall_le`) and introduce the new state binder, until the lattice type is\nno longer a function type. Returns `none` when the carrier is not a function type (nothing to\nintroduce); throws when the carrier is a function type that `le_of_forall_le` cannot peel, such as a\ndependent function lattice `(a : α) → β a → …`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introsExcessArgs","kind":"opaque","line":130,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introsExcessArgs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L130-L146"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.simpGoalTelescope\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">simpGoalTelescope</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Goal.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SimpGoalResult\">Meta.Sym.SimpGoalResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Simplify the goal's target with the configured hypothesis simp methods (a no-op without\n`Context.hypSimpMethods`), threading the persistent simp cache through `VCGenM`'s state.\n`.noProgress` is forwarded to the caller.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.simpGoalTelescope","kind":"def","line":117,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.simpGoalTelescope","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L117-L128"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introsHygienic\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">introsHygienic</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">overrides</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.toArray\">#[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.toArray\">]</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Introduce all leading binders of `goal` in one pass, naming the `i`-th binder `overrides[i]` when\ngiven and the binder's own name otherwise. Accessibility is decided by `tactic.hygienic` via\n`mkFreshBinderNameForTactic`. The introduction itself is a single `Sym.intros` call (which keeps\nthe memoized, sharing-correct intro); only the names are chosen here. Returns the goal unchanged\nwhen there are no leading binders.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introsHygienic","kind":"def","line":95,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introsHygienic","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L95-L115"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.processHypotheses\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">processHypotheses</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Goal\">Meta.Grind.Goal</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Goal\">Meta.Grind.Goal</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`Grind.processHypotheses` if `Context.internalize` is `true`, otherwise a no-op. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.processHypotheses","kind":"def","line":91,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.processHypotheses","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L91-L93"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule.applyChecked\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">BackwardRule</span>.<span class=\"name\">applyChecked</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">rule</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Apply.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule\">Meta.Sym.BackwardRule</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ruleDesc?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageData\">MessageData</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option.none\">none</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Apply.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.ApplyResult\">Meta.Sym.ApplyResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`VCGenM` wrapper around `BackwardRule.apply`. Behaves identically to\n`rule.apply goal` unless the application fails and `Context.debug` is on.\nIn that case it retries on a fresh metavariable whose type is the\n`unfoldReducible`-normalized goal type. If the retry succeeds, an earlier\nstep forgot a normalization; we throw a hard error pointing at the rule and\nthe missing reduction.\n\n`ruleDesc?` describes the rule for debug output. When `none`, the description\nis reconstructed from `rule.expr.getAppFn` — works for the common case of a\nconstant rule. Pass a custom message for dynamically-built rules.\n\nDesigned for dot notation: `rule.applyChecked goal`. Requires\n`open Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal` in scope so that the dot lookup resolves.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule.applyChecked","kind":"def","line":45,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule.applyChecked","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L45-L84"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule.shareCommon\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">BackwardRule</span>.<span class=\"name\">shareCommon</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">rule</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Apply.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule\">BackwardRule</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Apply.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule\">BackwardRule</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Internalize a backward rule's pattern into the current `SymM` share table. See\n`Pattern.shareCommon`. Designed for dot notation: `rule.shareCommon`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule.shareCommon","kind":"def","line":40,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule.shareCommon","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L40-L43"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.MVarId.replaceTargetDefEqFast\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">MVarId</span>.<span class=\"name\">replaceTargetDefEqFast</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">targetNew</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Change `goal`'s `Prop`-typed target to the definitionally-equal `targetNew`, mirroring the goal\nupdate in `Sym.Simp`: a fresh synthetic-opaque goal cast back through `@id`. Unlike\n`MVarId.replaceTargetDefEq` it skips the `instantiateMVars`/`Expr.equal` round-trip, so it neither\ndetects a no-op change nor supports a non-`Prop` target; the caller must pass a genuinely different\n`targetNew` definitionally equal to the current target. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.MVarId.replaceTargetDefEqFast","kind":"def","line":29,"name":"Lean.MVarId.replaceTargetDefEqFast","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L29-L38"}}],"imports":["Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Context","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Reduce","Lean.Meta.Sym.AlphaShareBuilder","Lean.Meta.Sym.Intro","Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Goal","Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Telescope","Lean.Meta.Sym.Util","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Main"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Util"}